title: Tukaloka Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Western, Take-out, Czech, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A cozy cafe where you can lounge in either a comfy chair, couch or hammock. Laid back/relaxed vibe. Serves coffee, teas or red espresso with a choice of at least 3 kinds of vegan milks. Satisfy your hunger with some in-house-made vegan snacks, soup and sweet or savory crepes. Full bar. Wi-fi. Non-smoking. Dog friendly.
